Cell["\<\
This section confirms consistency with the commutators presented in Equation \
blocks (12), (13), (14), and (15) of arXiv:2512.11796v2. The commutator \
evaluations are a nontrivial validation of the formulas for the matrix \
representations of operators.\
\>", "Text",
