Cell["Example calculations", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9747925536728783`*^9, 
  3.974792557988215*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"aede73bd-535b-4cfe-bb2c-\
27b80683743c"],

Cell["\<\
The Part I paper was concerned with the construction of the Hilbert space and \
its various degenerate/nondegenerate sectors characterized by the (P,Q) \
quantum numbers of the vertex legs. Calculations below are focused on the \
degenerate sectors. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.974792625757511*^9, 3.9747927036092787`*^9}, {
  3.9747927392262163`*^9, 3.974792810845261*^9}, {3.974792852671224*^9, 
  3.974792857732827*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dbc8efe5-7c04-4869-b91d-\
27fae8298ced"],

